snippet: Maya Moore scored 23 points, Rebekkah Brunson had 15 points and 12 rebounds, and the visiting Minnesota Lynx beat the Atlanta Dream to win their second W.N.B.A. title.
abstract: Minnesota Lynx beat Atlanta Dream, 86-77,  to win their second WNBA title in three years; other basketball news noted.
lead_paragraph: Maya Moore scored 23 points, Rebekkah Brunson had 15 points and 12 rebounds, and the visiting Minnesota Lynx beat the Atlanta Dream to win their second W.N.B.A. title.
